-- MOVES-Casey Quirk names Peter Chambers senior Europe adviser
-- By Ankit Ajmera in Bangalore
-- Thu Nov 06, 2014 01:44PM EST
-- None



Nov 6 (Reuters) - Management consulting firm Casey, Quirk & Associates LLC named Peter Chambers as a senior adviser for Europe.

Chambers was the chief executive of Legal & General Investment Management, the fund management business of British insurer Legal & General <LGEN.L>, and Framlington Group. He was also the chief investment officer at Gartmore Investment Ltd, said Casey Quirk, which serves the global asset management industry.